The paper deals with face sketch synthesis using deep learning, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The proposed method involves a semi-supervised learning approach, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of feature matching and patch-based representations also suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
